times has this happened so far?

355
00:17:03,083 --> 00:17:08,125
This would be
15,521 times so far.

356
00:17:08,208 --> 00:17:12,708
[KYON] Fifteen thousand
five-hundred twenty-one times?

357
00:17:12,791 --> 00:17:17,166
Wait... What do you
mean 15,521 times?

358
00:17:19,583 --> 00:17:21,916
