cashiers, we handed out--

371
00:17:58,166 --> 00:17:59,958
[KYON]
Okay! I got it...

372
00:18:05,125 --> 00:18:08,625
[KYON] Fifteen thousand
five-hundred twenty-one times...

373
00:18:08,708 --> 00:18:11,000
That's what Nagato said.

374
00:18:11,083 --> 00:18:14,416
Okay... So... times two weeks...

375
00:18:14,500 --> 00:18:19,625
That's, uh...
about... 595 years.

376
00:18:19,708 --> 00:18:22,791
She's the only one of us who
remembers everything we've done.

377
00:18:22,875 --> 00:18:27,041
And she's had to repeat those
same things over and over again.

378
00:18:27,125 --> 00:18:28,583
Nagato...

379
00:18:28,666 --> 00:18:32,625
What's it like to re-live the
same things that many times?

380
00:18:37,208 --> 00:18:39,583
That's gotta be the
craziest story ever.

381
00:18:41,375 --> 00:18:43,083
