I wonder if they're real.

382
00:18:43,166 --> 00:18:44,125
[KYON]
What's real?

383
00:18:44,208 --> 00:18:45,208
[HARUHI]
Martians.

384
00:18:45,291 --> 00:18:46,916
[KYON]
I kind of hope they aren't.

385
00:18:47,000 --> 00:18:49,458
I can't see anyone on
the surface right now,

386
00:18:49,541 --> 00:18:51,375
but I bet they're a
reserved race of beings

387
00:18:51,458 --> 00:18:53,041
who have to live underground.

388
00:18:53,125 --> 00:18:56,333
Whenever us humans are
finally able to land on Mars,

389
00:18:56,416 --> 00:18:58,875
I'm sure the Martians'll pop out
from wherever they're hiding,

390
00:18:58,958 --> 00:19:01,541
